# 6. Functional Requirements\
\
## FR-001\
\
### Visit Completion Trigger\
\
When a visit is marked as completed, the system automatically schedules a feedback request.\
\
Trigger\
\
- Visit Status = Completed\
\
Configurable Delay\
\
- Immediate\
- 2 Hours\
- 6 Hours\
- 24 Hours\
\
---\
\
